title: Chilling Adventures of Sabrina Season 2 Teaser Trailer Breakdown!
author: Think Story
comment: Someone know a spell to make it April 5th?
I’m just relieved there are going to be more hot warlocks next season
This isn't season 2. Its part 2 of season 1. The show was originally made for the CW with a 20 episode format. They are releasing part 2 of the first season.
I really do hope that this is not going to be the evil twin theory.  I really want Sabrina to go a little more darker this time around.
